com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data

Class URLActionDataStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.data.URLActionDataStore

  • public class URLActionDataStore
extends java.lang.Object

    Data container which holds all the necessary information to grab and store information out of a Http response in order to provide access to them via the interpreter.

    matthias
